GetFOV returns FOV part of given image using sensor data structure.

This function require image processing toolbox.

Parameters:

rescale flag if rescale to reconsruction matrix size have to be done 0 no, 1 yes (default value is 1)
threshold 0-without, other value - use it
method interpolating method for image rescaling (default is bilinear). For more see imresize help.
